ActCanada Revenue Agency Act
PrecisAppointment of THANE SHERRINGTON of Antigonish, Nova Scotia, to be a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Susan Hayes, whose term has expired.
